trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTableRow" /> objects that are the rows of an <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTable" /> control.

The <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTable.HtmlTableRowControlCollection> class represents a collection of <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTableRow> objects for an <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTable> control.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTable.HtmlTableRowControlCollection> 클래스의 컬렉션을 나타냅니다 <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTableRow> 에 대 한 개체는 <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTable> 제어 합니다.

trans-unit.source: Controls can be added at the end of the collection with the <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTable.HtmlTableRowControlCollection.Add%2A> method, or at a specified index location in the collection with the <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTable.HtmlTableRowControlCollection.AddAt%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: 컨트롤을 사용 하 여 컬렉션의 끝에 추가할 수 있습니다는 <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTable.HtmlTableRowControlCollection.Add%2A> 메서드를 사용 하 여 컬렉션의 지정한 인덱스 위치에 또는 <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTable.HtmlTableRowControlCollection.AddAt%2A> 메서드.

trans-unit.source: Only controls of type <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTableRow> can be added to the <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTable.HtmlTableRowControlCollection> collection.
trans-unit.target: 형식의 컨트롤만 <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTableRow> 에 추가할 수는 <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTable.HtmlTableRowControlCollection> 컬렉션입니다.

trans-unit.source: The following code example demonstrates how to create a custom <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTable.HtmlTableRowControlCollection> that overrides the <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTable.HtmlTableRowControlCollection.Add%2A> method so that when rows are added to a table, they are always added at the beginning of the table's row collection.
trans-unit.target: 다음 코드 예제에는 사용자 지정을 만드는 방법을 보여 줍니다 <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTable.HtmlTableRowControlCollection> 재정의 하는 <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTable.HtmlTableRowControlCollection.Add%2A> 메서드 행 테이블에 추가 될 때, 되도록 항상 테이블의 행 컬렉션의 시작 부분에 추가 됩니다.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Control" /> to add to the collection.
Adds the specified <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Control" /> object to the collection.
The added control can only be an <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTableRow> control; otherwise, an <xref:System.ArgumentException> exception is thrown.
trans-unit.target: 추가 된 컨트롤은만 될 수 있습니다는 <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTableRow> 컨트롤 그렇지는 <xref:System.ArgumentException> 예외가 throw 됩니다.

trans-unit.source: The following code example demonstrates how to create a custom <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTable.HtmlTableRowControlCollection> collection that overrides the <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTable.HtmlTableRowControlCollection.Add%2A> method so that when rows are added to a table, they are always added at the beginning of the table's row collection.
trans-unit.target: 다음 코드 예제에는 사용자 지정을 만드는 방법을 보여 줍니다 <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTable.HtmlTableRowControlCollection> 를 재정의 하는 컬렉션의 <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTable.HtmlTableRowControlCollection.Add%2A> 메서드 행 테이블에 추가 될 때, 되도록 항상 테이블의 행 컬렉션의 시작 부분에 추가 됩니다.

trans-unit.source: Notice how the custom <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTable.HtmlTableRowControlCollection.Add%2A> method calls the base class's <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTable.HtmlTableRowControlCollection.AddAt%2A> method with the `index` parameter equal to 0.
trans-unit.target: 알림 방법을 사용자 지정 <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTable.HtmlTableRowControlCollection.Add%2A> 기본 클래스의 메서드를 호출 <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTable.HtmlTableRowControlCollection.AddAt%2A> 사용 하 여 메서드는 `index` 매개 변수를 0입니다.

trans-unit.source: The added control must be of type <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTableRow" />.
The location in the array at which to add the child control.
The <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Control" /> to add to the collection.
Adds the specified <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Control" /> object to the collection.
The new control is added to the array at the specified index location.
trans-unit.target: 새 컨트롤은 지정된 인덱스 위치의 배열에 추가됩니다.

trans-unit.source: The added control can only be an <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTableRow> control; otherwise, an <xref:System.ArgumentException> is thrown.
trans-unit.target: 추가 된 컨트롤은만 될 수 있습니다는 <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTableRow> 컨트롤 그렇지는 <xref:System.ArgumentException> throw 됩니다.

trans-unit.source: The added control must be of type <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTableRow" />.
